snippet.textDisplay:
Bol! Ke Lub Aazaad Hain Tere [Speak! for Your Lips (Lub) Are Free!]
Bol! Zubaan Ab Tak Teree Hai [Speak! Your Tongue Is Still Yours!]
Teraa Sutwaan Jism Hai Teraa [Your Clean-Slim (Sutwaan) Body (Jism) Is Yours!]
Bol! Ke Jaan Ab Tak Teree Hai [Speak! Your Life Is Still Yours!]
Dekh Ke Aahangar Ki Dukaan Mein [See! How in the Blacksmith's (Aahangar’s) Shop]
Tund Hain Shole; Surkh Hai Aahan [The Flames Are Fierce and Hot (Tund)! The Iron (Aahan) Is Red (Hot)!]
Khulne Lage Quflon Ke Dahaane [Mouths (Dahaane) of Locks (Qufl) Have Begun to Open]
Phaila Har-Ek Zanjeer Kaa Daaman [Each Chain's Skirt (Daaman) Has Spread Wide!]
Bol! Ye Thodaa Saa Waqt Bahut Hai [Speak! This Little Time Is Plenty]
Jism-o-Zubaan Ki Maut Se Pahle [Before the Death of Body and Tongue]
Bol! Ke Sach Zinda Hai Ab Tak  [Speak! For Truth Is Still Alive]
Bol! Jo Kuchh Kahna Hai Kahle! [Speak! Say! Whatever Must Be Said]

snippet.textDisplay:
फ़ैज़ अहमद फ़ैज़ की नज़्म “बोल”
बोल! के लब आज़ाद हैं तेरे
बोल! ज़ुबाँ अब तक तेरी है

(सुत्वाँ = तराशाहुवा, साफ़-सुथरा, दुबला-पतला)

तेरा सुत्वाँ जिस्म है तेरा 
बोल! के जाँ अब तक तेरी है

आहन-गर = लोहार 

देख! के आहन-गर की दुकाँ में
तुंद हैं शोले, सुर्ख़ है आहन

तुंद =तेज़, उग्र, भीषण।    सुर्ख़ =लाल‍।    आहन = लोहा 

क़ुफ़्ल = ताला। दहान = मूंह्।   क़ुफ़्लों के दहाने = तालों के मूंह्
खुलने लगे क़ुफ़्लों के दहाने
फैला हर-इक ज़ंजीर का दामन

बोल! ये थोड़ा वक़्त बहोत है
जिस्मो-ज़ुबाँ की मौत से पहले
बोल! के सच ज़िंदा है अब तक
बोल! जो कुछ कैह्ना है, कैह् ले

snippet.textDisplay: It's an honor and privilege to listen to this wonderful rendition of such a famous poet's words! My heartfelt thanks to Coke Studio Pakistan for  presenting this beautiful composition through Shafqat Amanat Ali Khan. Done full justice to the sentiments of the words! Hope CS continues for years to come. It's a lifeline for many music lovers like me. And hats off to the entire team of musicians and backup vocals. They actually make this entire presentation look so effortless and yet classy! Salute to the entire CSP from India 👍
